[{"location":"lib/Methods/#Methods","page":"Methods","title":"Methods","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#Index","page":"Methods","title":"Index","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"lib/Methods/","page":"Methods","title":"Methods","text":"Pages = [\"Methods.md\"]","category":"page"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#Gadget2","page":"Methods","title":"Gadget2","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"lib/Methods/","page":"Methods","title":"Methods","text":"read_gadget2\nread_gadget2_pos\nwrite_gadget2\nwrite_gadget2_format2\nload(::Stream{format\"Gadget2\"})\nsave(::Stream{format\"Gadget2\"})","category":"page"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#AstroIO.read_gadget2","page":"Methods","title":"AstroIO.read_gadget2","text":"read_gadget2(filename::AbstractString, units, fileunits = uGadget2; kw...)\n\nReturn a Tuple of header and particle data in snapshot file. units is supported by PhysicalParticles: uSI, uCGS, uAstro, uGadget2, nothing. fileunits is the internal units in the file, and will be converted to units while reading the file.\n\nKeywords\n\nacc::Bool = false : read acceleration data if exist\npot::Bool = false : read potential data if exist\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#AstroIO.read_gadget2_pos","page":"Methods","title":"AstroIO.read_gadget2_pos","text":"read_gadget2_pos(filename::AbstractString, units, fileunits = uGadget2)\n\nOnly read position block and return a StructArray.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#AstroIO.write_gadget2","page":"Methods","title":"AstroIO.write_gadget2","text":"writegadget2(filename::AbstractString, header::HeaderGadget2, data::AbstractArray, units = uGadget2; format2 = true, kw...) writegadget2(filename::AbstractString, data, units = uGadget2; kw...)\n\nWrite particle data to file. units are supported by PhysicalParticles: uSI, uCGS, uAstro, uGadget2, nothing. Gadget2 header is automatedly generated if not provided.\n\nKeywords\n\nformat2 = true: if true, write in format-2 of Gadget2 snapshot\nacc::Bool = false : write acceleration data\npot::Bool = false : write potential data\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#AstroIO.write_gadget2_format2","page":"Methods","title":"AstroIO.write_gadget2_format2","text":"write_gadget2_format2(filename::AbstractString, header::HeaderGadget2, data::AbstractArray, units = uGadget2; kw...)\nwrite_gadget2_format2(filename::AbstractString, data, units = uGadget2; kw...)\n\nWrite particle data to format-2 Gadget2 snapshot file. units are supported by PhysicalParticles: uSI, uCGS, uAstro, uGadget2, nothing. Gadget2 header is automatedly generated if not provided.\n\nKeywords\n\nacc::Bool = false : write acceleration data\npot::Bool = false : write potential data\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#JLD2","page":"Methods","title":"JLD2","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"lib/Methods/","page":"Methods","title":"Methods","text":"read_jld\nread_gadget2_jld\nwrite_jld\nwrite_gadget2_jld","category":"page"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#Tools","page":"Methods","title":"Tools","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"lib/Methods/","page":"Methods","title":"Methods","text":"renamesuffixs\nrenamereplace","category":"page"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#AstroIO.renamesuffixs","page":"Methods","title":"AstroIO.renamesuffixs","text":"function renamesuffixs(folder::AbstractString, namebase::AbstractString, suffix::AbstractString)\n\nReplace the end of all files whose name contain namebase with suffix.\n\nExample\n\nFor files test_1.middle.txt and test_2.middle.txt, with command\n\nrenamesuffixs(\"./\", \"test\", \".csv\")\n\nwe will get test_1.middle.csv and test_2.middle.csv\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"lib/Methods/#AstroIO.renamereplace","page":"Methods","title":"AstroIO.renamereplace","text":"function renamereplace(folder::AbstractString, old::AbstractString, new::AbstractString; kw...)\n\nReplace string old in all files to new. Keywords kw... are passed to replace\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/#Gadget2-I/O","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"The default units in Gadget-2 snapshots are collected as uGadget2. However, it is much more convenient to use uAstro in simulations:","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"using PhysicalParticles, AstroIO\nuGadget2\nuAstro","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/#Basic-usage","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Basic usage","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"Units are automatedly converted during I/O:","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"# read default uGadget2 units from file and convert to uAstro\nheader, data = read_gadget2(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro);\n\n# manually set the units in snapshot file\nheader, data = read_gadget2(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro, uGadget2);\n\n# read default uGadget2 units from file and convert to unitless\nheader, data = read_gadget2(\"snapshot.gadget2\", nothing, uGadget2);\n\n# write in default uGadget2 units\nwrite_gadget2(\"output.Gadget2\", header, data)\n\n# write in uAstro units\nwrite_gadget2(\"output.Gadget2\", header, data, uAstro)\n# and read in uAstro units\nheader, data = read_gadget2(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro, uAstro);","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"Be careful with these unit conversions!","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"In some cases (for example, visualization), it is more efficient to only read position data from file:","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"read_gadget2_pos(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro)\nread_gadget2_pos(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro, uGadget2)","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/#FileIO-interfaces","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"FileIO interfaces","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"FileIO provides load and save interfaces to I/O snapshots:","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/gadget2/","page":"Gadget2 I/O","title":"Gadget2 I/O","text":"header, data = load(\"snapshot.gadget2\")\nsave(\"FileIO.gadget2\", header, data)\n\nheader, data = load(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro, uGadget2)\nsave(\"FileIO.gadget2\", header, data, uGadget2)","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Package-Guide","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Installation","page":"Package Guide","title":"Installation","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"From the Julia REPL, type ] to enter the Pkg REPL mode and run","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"pkg> add AstroIO","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"or add from git repository","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"pkg> add https://github.com/JuliaAstroSim/AstroIO.jl","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"Test the package by","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"pkg> test AstroIO","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Basic-Usage","page":"Package Guide","title":"Basic Usage","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"using AstroIO","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Gadget2","page":"Package Guide","title":"Gadget2","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"Suffixes gadget2, Gadget2, GADGET2 are supported","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"header, data = read_gadget2(\"snapshot.gadget2\", uAstro)\n\nwrite_gadget2(\"output.Gadget2\", header, data)\n\n# If only data provided, a default header would be generated\nwrite_gadget2(\"output.GADGET2\", data)","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"Supported units: uAstro, uGadget2, uSI, uCSG.","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Use-FileIO-interfaces","page":"Package Guide","title":"Use FileIO interfaces","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"header, data = load(\"snapshot.gadget2\")\nsave(\"FileIO.gadget2\", header, data)","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Output-CSV","page":"Package Guide","title":"Output CSV","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"write_csv(\"output\", csv) # No suffix","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/guide/#Save-and-load-with-JLD2","page":"Package Guide","title":"Save and load with JLD2","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/guide/","page":"Package Guide","title":"Package Guide","text":"write_gadget2_jld(\"output.jld2\", header, data, uGadget2)\nwrite_jld(\"NoHeader.jld2\", data)\n\nheader, data = read_gadget2_jld(\"output.jld2\")\ndata = read(\"NoHeader.jld2\")\n\n# Or simply use JLD2 interfaces\n@load \"NoHeader.jld2\"","category":"page"},{"location":"#AstroIO.jl","page":"Home","title":"AstroIO.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"File I/O interfaces for astrophysical simulations","category":"page"},{"location":"#Package-Feature","page":"Home","title":"Package Feature","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"FileIO.jl interfaces\nSupported formats:\nGadget-2\nJLD2\nCSV\nHDF5 (work in progress)","category":"page"},{"location":"#Manual-Outline","page":"Home","title":"Manual Outline","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"manual/tools/#Tools","page":"Tools","title":"Tools","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"manual/tools/","page":"Tools","title":"Tools","text":"renamesuffixs\nrenamereplace","category":"page"}]
